I"#<p><em>de/ter|       |ior.ation</em> was written in early March 2015 and is closely tied to my multimedia opera Hunger, exploring themes of psychological decay, irrationality, &amp; self-destruction through fragmentation of musical objects, gestures, video, &amp; obfuscation. […] These themes are manifest in the character of the musical materials themselves, navigating a spectrum between saturation &amp; fragility. I imagine this almost as an estranged overture to the opera - existing separately, but remaining inextricably entwined…</p>
